body:
Dear Riot, when I got Warring Kingdoms Nidalee today, I tryed her out, and from watching a PBE Commentary I saw that the Hunted Symbol was Red. When playing her, the Hunted was yellow again. Would it be nice to change the color back to Red because the Chinese New Year uses the Red to make the devil fear and make it go away. This way, in the game, the skin should still include the Red Hunted for the synbolism. When I came across this, I felt bad because the Yellow doesn't really go with the skin and doesn't really make sense.

Thanks

 {{champion:76}} 
                  
